item.itunes:summary:
Randy Mack of Domaine Real Estate Presents 2202 Sunlit Avenue Drive, Santa Rosa CA 95403.
This home is an immaculate North West Santa Rosa Gem with amazing curb appeal! The 3 bedroom 2 bath residence is located in the heart of beautiful Sonoma County California. This gorgeous single level home features 3 full bedrooms, a spacious master bath with numerous appointments, and even a full second bathroom!
A brick fireplace in the living room really cozies up the house and is ideal for entertaining, with plenty of usable living and dining space for you and your guests. The master suite opens to the beautifully landscaped rear yard, complete with a green house and ample backyard room to play as well as a covered porch for relaxing and Sunday lounging.
With additional spaces of an indoor laundry room and a full second bedroom, 2202 Sunlit Ann is move in Ready!
For more information, please contact Randy Mack by phone at (707) 824-2260 or visit Domaine Real Estate online at www.esonomahomes.com
